<br>
So I was wondering what might be some good guilds to look into?  <br>
<br>
I'm an evil oracle who knows what he's doing... <br>
<br>
I like to raid, and I like to lead raids...<br>
<br>
With college starting and life back in tact, I *refuse* to guarentee 80% raid attendance.  So it looks like  no raiding guilds for me.  Chances are I'd make most raids but ... life &gt; than eq.<br>
<br>
As opposed to guilding, should I just stay guildless and lead a life of open raiding?<br>
<br>
Any input on the matter would be great.  Thanks.<br>
