<br>
I am definately not trying to con you into joining my guild as we are just starting and I still haven't got my 10 tagged (*taps her foot at the missing people who haven't logged on in a week*).  Just my 2 cp on how I go about finding my place in guilds on EverQuest.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
