If you're looking for a guild, I'd strongly reccomend looking into Dreadstorm.  Just to restate/add a few points, we're a fairly high end guild in a fairly unique spot on the high-end scale (above a lot of the 'lower high end' and high enough to do some of the things/mobs the three other 'high end' guidls do); we kill/do a lot of the mobs/things that you seem to be interested in trying (Kunark dragons, the Va'Dyn, Halls of Testing, etc; working on/very close to other things in that kind of range - UP bosses, Rhaggs, etc).  We look primarialy for cool and skilled players who know their class and the game well, and who're interested in having fun over loot and a heavy raiding schedule (although our raids are gradually increasing).<br>
