<br>
The DS raid schedule is pretty much cemented, we have a fixed guild raid on saturday (generally a big time comitment raid like one of the planes or HoT) and we do epic raids on the sunday. Friday nights are generally left for impromtue luclin boss mobs (depending on who is up). For each of the raids above we generally have 20-30 guild members attend.<br>
<br>
Our weekday raids however are very much pickup... if we have enough people on who are bored of grinding.... we will pick a target and go off and do it... if not people will continue grinding.<br>
<br>
I very much doubt that DS will start scheduling regular weekday raids like the big 3(2), this is one the things that set us apart from them. If you wish to find a guild that has a 24/7 raid schedule then I would suggest looking elsewhere.<br>
