<br>
As far as raiding goes, we raid every Saturday and Sunday, and hit single encounter dragons, luclin mobs or whatever two or three times during the course of the week.  Saturdays our raids typically will focus on strengthening the guild. Sundays, we raid for member epics. That could be a single planar raid, or multiple epic quest targets throughout Norrath.<br>
<br>
And yes we have very little potty talk. <p><CENTER>

